			<!-- Section heading -->
			<h3 class="h1 h2-mb  mb-3  text-black fw-bold lh-sm">Working Capital Loan</h3>
			<p class="mb-4">We offer the funds to sustain your business while your physical cash is not enough for capital turnover in the business. A working capital loan is suitable for a business when retained earnings for inventory, account receivable turnover, or cash conversion cycle which has been obstructed.</p>
			
