			<!-- Section heading -->
			<h3 class="h1 h2-mb  mb-3  text-black fw-bold lh-sm">Investment Loan</h3>
			<p class="mb-4">The investment loan is for borrowers who need funds to expand their business. You can purchase/upgrade your business premise, store, factory and equipment or acquire a business to complement and enhance your current business.</p>
			
